title: eJay Techno 3 v1.01.0009-CHAOS [deepstatus]
description:
eJay Techno 3 v1.01.0009










CREATE THE ULTIMATE PARTY SOUNDTRACK IN MINUTES! 4 000 current sounds & loops direct from the eJay sound studios for use in your own hits. The latest sounds in Hi-Fi stereo quality. Refine your track with the FX Studio and the drum computer! Generate your own sequences and grooves with the Hyper Generator III. The in-built Music Animator will create animations to suit your dance mix. Start making music now!


4 000 current sounds & loops direct from the eJay sound studios for use in your own hits.

32 track Sound Mixer in Hi-Fi stereo quality

Hyper Generator lll - revolutionary synthesizer

Equalizer, booster and audio mixer

Live Music Animator with Save to Mix

Export your mix as a WAVE file

Easy to use, full drag & drop support

More than 4 000 royalty-free Techno samples

Record your own samples via microphone

Import /export sounds

Time Stretcher for simple speed-adjustment




_______________________________________________________________________________________________



   System Requirements

Windows 7/Vista/XP, DirectX 8.1, 1,5 GHz processor, 512 MB Memory, 680 MB Hard Disk Space




[Installation]

UnRar.

Install ejay_techno3_setup.
( choose proper lang in setup window )

Don't launch yet.

Copy the content from Patch folder to installation directory

x64: C:Program Files (x86)eJayTechno 3
x86: C:Program FileseJayTechno 3
